      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at some photos of the deep field from the webb telescope... everything is so far away and so old and it just makes everything i'm doing feel like such a joke. like why even bother waking up tomorrow when the sun is just gonna burn out anyway and none of this matters? it all feels so pointless.",
