      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"constructed meaning\" feels so fake though. like, its just a coping mechanism to stop us from realizing we are just biological accidents on a rock that's destined to be nothing. if everything is temporary and eventually everything disappears, why does the \"value of today\" even matter? it feels like i'm just performing a play that's going to be cancelled anyway.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
